{"tid":1449964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:15:13.000Z","uid":17878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"faf14e407772c72ef4af485974569887d8c63923","tid":1449964,"uid":17878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:12:43.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=996f5add\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpjvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=4254b790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"bf0bf72e204ba4fda803c6a48f1beadd18f913e8","tid":1449964,"uid":17878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0BmwaFY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0BmwaFY.jpg&h=9b990334&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e7244f08194d746bc597941a3e99e8bf5ec4456","tid":1449964,"uid":67605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:15:13.000Z","msg":"不要說推，請說<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n6. 警犬在太古站推人落電梯"}]}